    Celso)
  * support shorthand syntax for PPAs (ppa:owner or
    ppa:owner/ppa_name) when clicking on "add"
  * support new commandline option "--enable-ppa name"

 -- Michael Vogt <michael.vogt@ubuntu.com>  Mon, 08 Jun 2009 18:28:24 +0200

